{"3192280": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "密室遊戲決鬥～今天誰會買走我的女友～", "steam_appid": 3192280, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ 遊戲簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「如果沒有辦法在遊戲中獲勝，取得逃出去的鑰匙，就會被永遠關在這個密室！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >終於鼓起勇氣向暗戀許久的青梅竹馬告白，成為了戀人。<br>一回過神，卻發現自己與女朋友，還有另外三個男人，一同被關在了神秘的密室，被迫要進行遊戲對決。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/d83064af7bf9e14713cc22e68d4b644d.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而唯一能逃脫這個密室的方式，就是不斷在遊戲中獲得勝利，賺取足夠的點數買到兩人份的逃生的鑰匙。然而在這個密室遊戲當中，獲得的點數什麼東西都可以購買—也包括了他人的所有權。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清純的亞里沙是一個出身名門的千金小姐，對於異性缺乏邊界感，也對性懵懂無知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同樣被關在密室中的另外三個男人，卻似乎對買到逃生鑰匙興致缺缺，反而不停試圖接近亞里沙。一場1 VS 3 的密室逃脫 &amp; NTR防衛戰就此展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/7a57e2aad0ee181598b1e8023e2f7e5d.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1280 height=768 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ 遊戲玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家必須要與三位男性參賽者進行遊戲對戰，不斷獲勝賺取點數，購買逃生鑰匙帶著女友逃離密室。遊戲對戰有「撲克牌」、「倒數」、「猜數字」三種遊戲可以選擇。每一個男性參賽者各自有擅長的遊戲項目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎撲克牌：</strong>五張撲克牌手牌，在雙方開牌前可以決定有哪幾張要換牌重抽。每張牌只能替換一次。最後雙方開牌，看誰組出的牌型大小更大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/12aab79a13c91bc7fce451364d28a5ec.poster.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1170 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/12aab79a13c91bc7fce451364d28a5ec.webm?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/12aab79a13c91bc7fce451364d28a5ec.mp4?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎倒數：</strong>雙方按順序抽取編號從三十號到零號的牌。自己的回合時可以選擇抽一、二、或是三張牌。最後抽到零號牌人的輸。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/209ec89b47946de99c1edf5788791d86.poster.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1170 height=776 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/209ec89b47946de99c1edf5788791d86.webm?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/209ec89b47946de99c1edf5788791d86.mp4?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎猜數字：</strong>三位數的數字密碼，要在十回合內，透過位數一致、數字一致等提示，推理直到猜出正確的數字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/49c880c7a897c6cd02309bcbe8c0a949.poster.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/49c880c7a897c6cd02309bcbe8c0a949.webm?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/49c880c7a897c6cd02309bcbe8c0a949.mp4?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果玩家在對戰中輸掉的話，其他男性參賽者就會使用點數來購買亞里沙的三日所有權。那麼接下來的三天，亞里沙就必須和他同進同出。就連晚上也會同房度過…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在房間當中，究竟發生了什麼樣的事呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/992e417e95ed17663fbff30c534ad43b.poster.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1170 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/992e417e95ed17663fbff30c534ad43b.webm?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/992e417e95ed17663fbff30c534ad43b.mp4?t=1776755784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼</strong> <strong>角色介紹</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/e10b3c9c17ca4662640b15f947b7940b.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><strong>▼ 遊戲特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與每個男主角以外的男人都有9個H場景，共7張HCG與其差分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >男主角（玩家）徹頭徹尾都是NTR苦主，適合喜歡NTR劇情的玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >買到鑰匙除了與女友一同逃脫的Happy End之外，還可以有其他的多元選擇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任一結局通關一次後即可解鎖全回想。</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ 遊戲簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「如果沒有辦法在遊戲中獲勝，取得逃出去的鑰匙，就會被永遠關在這個密室！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >終於鼓起勇氣向暗戀許久的青梅竹馬告白，成為了戀人。<br>一回過神，卻發現自己與女朋友，還有另外三個男人，一同被關在了神秘的密室，被迫要進行遊戲對決。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/d83064af7bf9e14713cc22e68d4b644d.avif?t=1776755784\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而唯一能逃脫這個密室的方式，就是不斷在遊戲中獲得勝利，賺取足夠的點數買到兩人份的逃生的鑰匙。然而在這個密室遊戲當中，獲得的點數什麼東西都可以購買—也包括了他人的所有權。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清純的亞里沙是一個出身名門的千金小姐，對於異性缺乏邊界感，也對性懵懂無知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同樣被關在密室中的另外三個男人，卻似乎對買到逃生鑰匙興致缺缺，反而不停試圖接近亞里沙。一場1 VS 3 的密室逃脫 &amp; NTR防衛戰就此展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192280/extras/7a57e2aad0e